Name: Fix My Cat Doc
About the game: Welcome to the world of cats! Fix My Cat Doc game is a simulator in which you are acting as a veterinarian. Your mission is to save as many animals as possible from torment and pain. You have to be very careful because pet owners trust you a lot. Try not to disappoint them. Good Luck ! Game Features : - More than 8 hospitals - Coins collector every 2 hours - A lot of cats which you have to treat
